- Sheet renders list of unreachable agents with emoji, color dot, name, status badge, runtime badge, and last-seen time
- Shows empty state with green checkmark when no unreachable agents exist
- Each agent shows its `useAgentVisual` identity (emoji + color)
- Handles agents with no `lastSeenAt` gracefully (no timestamp shown)
- Handles agents with no `runtime` gracefully (no runtime badge)
